      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "PROMPT STUDIO + GEMINI + HASH VAULT — generate a styled image from a creative brief, with full caching and style-aware cache keys.\n\nFLOW\nThe Prompt Studio Settings node is the single source of truth for the photographer style. Its STRING output drives BOTH Prompt Studio's converted-to-input style slot AND Hash Vault's any_input_2 slot. Brief drives Hash Vault's payload_string. So the cache key = (brief + style). Re-run with the same brief AND same style → hit, $0.00 billed. Change either one → new hash → Prompt Studio enhances, Gemini generates, Save persists.\n\nLAZY BYPASS: on a cache hit, the Lazy API Switch demands ONLY the cached_data branch. Prompt Studio + Gemini + Save never execute, so no Flash and no Pro Image cost.\n\nSTYLE: pick a photographer on the Prompt Studio Settings dropdown. The DNA prompt for that photographer is fed to Gemini Flash via Prompt Studio, which expands your brief into an authentic styled prompt. This is the GENERATION path — use it when you want a fresh image in a photographer's voice. (Style Transfer is the other path: image-in → image-out polish, only works when source DNA is close to target.)\n\nLABEL BUILDER auto-formats the Hash Vault label as 'brief / style' so the Browser shows what was generated. Both inputs are wired upstream so the label always reflects the actual generation parameters — nothing to keep in sync manually.\n\nREQUIRES: ComfyUI-API-Optimizer >= 1.4.2 (Hash Vault + Label Builder), ComfyUI-Gemini-Direct >= 1.2.0 (Prompt Studio + Prompt Studio Settings + Gemini Image Generate), ComfyUI-KJNodes (StringConstantMultiline). Gemini API key in gemini_api_key.txt at ComfyUI root."
      ]
    },
